data.address: 511 Florida Boulevard (Jarboe Park), Neptune Beach, FL 32266
data.details: Explore the outdoors, make a craft, play a game, and sing songs during this fun filled day! Plus, you get to participate in activities run by middle school Girl Scouts who just completed Program Aide Training! This event is perfect to come on your own or with your Girl Scout Brownie troop. This event costs $5 per girl.
